an class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> Explicit methods of order 7 wi=
th 9 stages<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Butcher_1965_408_11-2" class=3D"reference"><=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Runge%E2%80%93Kutta_methods#cite_no=
