<p>The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Runge%E2%80%93Kutta%E2%80%9=
3Fehlberg_method" title=3D"Runge=E2=80=93Kutta=E2=80=93Fehlberg method">Run=
ge=E2=80=93Kutta=E2=80=93Fehlberg method</a> has two methods of orders 5 an=
d 4. Its extended Butcher tableau is:
</p>
<table cellspacing=3D"0" cellpadding=3D"3">
