<p>However, the simplest adaptive Runge=E2=80=93Kutta method involves combi=
ning <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heun%27s_method" title=3D"Heu=
n's method">Heun's method</a>, which is order 2, with the <a href=3D"https:=
//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euler_method" title=3D"Euler method">Euler method</=
a>, which is order 1. Its extended Butcher tableau is:
</p>
<table cellspacing=3D"0" cellpadding=3D"3">
