-align: -0.671ex; width:7.454ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle y'=
=3D\lambda y}"></span>. A Runge=E2=80=93Kutta method applied to this equati=
on reduces to the iteration <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-elemen=
