\lambda )\,y_{n}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/7438624523406321db174cf6242c896c153f5c9a" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
